con:config.con:query: SELECT M.INITIATORID,M.INITIATORBANKID,M.CUSTOMERID,TRANSACTIONSID,M.AGREEMENTID,PAYMENTINFOID,HT.DEBETACCOUNTNO,PAYMENTSTATUS,INSTRUCTEDAMOUNT,M.MESSAGEIDENTIFICATION FROM MESSAGE M INNER JOIN PAYMENTINFO PI ON M.MESSAGEID = PI.FK_MESSAGEID INNER JOIN TRANSACTIONS HT ON PI.PAYMENTINFOID = HT.FK_PAYMENTINFOID WHERE M.INITIATORBANKID='4201' and M.ORIGINALFORMAT='PMUL' AND PAYMENTSTATUS='RFDD' ORDER BY TRANSACTIONSID DESC fetch first row only
